## Requirements File (requirements.txt)
```
python-whois
requests
python-dotenv
beautifulsoup4
shodan
```

## Security Notes
- Implements input sanitization to prevent injection attacks
- Uses environment variables for secure API key management
- Includes logging for tracking tool usage
